  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "🍗 SERVICE CREW (FULL TIME)",
  "description": "<p>Are you a food lover with a big smile and bigger energy?<br>\nCrave is on the lookout for enthusiastic and customer-focused individuals to join our team! We’re proud to serve Singapore’s favourite Nasi Lemak and local delights 🇸🇬✨</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>What You’ll Do:</strong><br>\n🍗 Prepare and serve our signature Crave Nasi Lemak, satay and other delights with pride<br>\n🎯 Perform cashiering duties and handle customer transactions accurately<br>\n😊 Deliver friendly, top-notch service – every customer, every time<br>\n🧼 Keep the store clean, hygienic, and organized</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>What We’re Looking For:</strong><br>\n✔ No F&amp;B experience? No problem – we’ll train you!<br>\n✔ Valid Food Hygiene Certificate preferred (Don’t worry – we’ll send you if you don’t have it)<br>\n✔ Able to work weekends, evenings, and Public Holidays<br>\n✔ Fast learner, team player, and service-oriented<br>\n✔ Basic English</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Why Join Us?</strong><br>\n✨ Career progression with training provided<br>\n✨ Sales incentives of up to $300<br>\n✨ Fun and supportive work environment<br>\n✨ Staggered working hours<br>\n✨ Staff meals (yes, nasi lemak perks!)<br>\n<br>\nWhether you’re serving fragrant coconut rice or greeting customers with a smile, you’ll be part of making every meal a memorable Crave experience.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Apply now and let’s spread the love for Nasi Lemak together!</p>",
